Package: bushfirerisk
Title: Bushfire Climate Drivers for Southeast Australia
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Yuehan",
      family = "Zhou",
      email = "yzho0318@student.monash.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Package(educational) for ETC5523 Assignment 4.
    Provides a cleaned monthly climate dataset ('bushfire_real')
    for southeast Australia (1979-2020), plus helper plotting
    functions and a Shiny app launcher. The goal is to explore
    temperature, wind, and dryness as drivers of bushfire risk.
